remarks: Ordering on reals satisfies strict trichotomy.  Axiom 18 of 22 for real and complex numbers, justified by theorem ~ axpre-lttri .  Note:  The more general version for extended reals is ~ axlttri .  Normally new proofs would use ~ xrlttri .  (New usage is discouraged.)  (Contributed by NM, 13-Oct-2005.)
statement: ax-pre-lttri $p |- ( ( A e. RR /\ B e. RR ) -> ( A <RR B <-> -. ( A = B \/ B <RR A ) ) ) $.
